>> return a nonzero value if the device is the primary display.
> 
>> +static inline int fb_is_primary_device(struct fb_screeninfo *info)
>                                                  ^^^^^^^^^^^^^
Yikes, thanks.  Andrew, here's an updated patch.
Tony
